        "created_at": "2022-10-23T03:35:00.422Z",
        "cooked": "<p>What a fantastic beautiful bottle of wine.  Despite being from a different appellation and a different cepage, this have more than just a little bit of Rayas magic in it.  Mid to pale red. The nose smells like Rayas with perfumed wild strawberries and some spice.  Palate is not as deep and powerful as a Rayas but it reminds me of Rayas a lot.Lots of those red berry fruits with a bit of white pepper, fine tannins and a lovely kiss of acidity making is fresh and delicious.   This is all elegance and  balance and grace.  Nice long finish   This is  dangerously drinkable and moreish.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/3X/1/b/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3\" title=\"20221023_164553\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/1/b/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3_2_281x500.jpeg\" alt=\"20221023_164553\" data-base62-sha1=\"3ZxYW25tmJIc0hDeuDyQKsl6ZMv\" width=\"281\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/1/b/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3_2_281x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/1/b/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3_2_421x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/3X/1/b/1bfb9e74353d5befddbf71df8bf2122fafb874d3_2_562x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"766C65\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">20221023_164553</span><span class=\"informations\">1920\u00d73413 329 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Brodie</p>",
